Package: OMOPPregnancy
Type: Package
Title: Pregnancy Episode Identification in OMOP CDM Using HIPPS Algorithm
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-01-12
Authors@R: c(
    person("Package", "Maintainer", email = "maintainer@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Louisa H", "Smith", role = "ctb", comment = "Original All of Us implementation"),
    person("Sara E", "Jones", role = "ctb", comment = "Original HIPPS algorithm")
    )
Description: Implements the HIPPS (Hierarchy and rule-based pregnancy episode 
    Inference integrated with Pregnancy Progression Signatures) algorithm for 
    identifying pregnancy episodes in OMOP CDM databases. This package enables 
    cross-site comparison studies and benchmarking of pregnancy identification 
    across different OMOP CDM implementations, including All of Us and other 
    healthcare databases.
